1.0.name: wordpress/video-sidebar-widgets
1.0.description: A collection of sidebar widgets for displaying Flash Videos from 14 video sharing networks. Video networks includes Youtube, Vimeo, BlipTV, Google, etc. This plugin consist of 2 widgets and 1 TinyMCE editor button.
